				<wikidot:authorName>BvS-Uzuki</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>78144</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Here's the deal. The day we enter the Ninja World War, we get 2 of each resource. (2 crystals, 2 metals, 2 waters). I want to spend those <em>immediately</em> upon entering the war. Since we'll have pretty minimal defense when we start up (and since this forum is pretty open for anyone to see), we'll be a pretty ripe target for losing those.</p> <p>Here are the options for those resources, best I can tell.</p> <p><a href="http://bvs.wikidot.com/upgrade:jonin-council">Jonin Council</a> - Need 20 people, 100,000 ryo.<br /> <a href="http://bvs.wikidot.com/upgrade:black-market">Black Market</a> - Need 20 people, 10,000 ryo.</p> <p>We should be able to afford both of these the day we go on the market, assuming we pick up 7 more people in the next week or so. Any objection to these?</p> <p><strong>Edited</strong>: I did the math wrong on the War Room, sorry if you read the earlier version of this.</p> 
				 	]]>
